    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "Hi @timkelty thanks for challenging the APIs we propose.\r\n\r\nThe connectors were created in order to provide this kind of flexibility. As I see things right now, providing a new API that is so specifically dedicated to templates will reinforce their usage. I think the balance of power of the template API, the simplicity of it and the impact on the code of the project is right. I will however sync back with the whole InstantSearch team to get their feelings too.",
